00:23:04,950 --> 00:23:07,120
He doesn't need that old hag anymore.

496
00:23:08,187 --> 00:23:10,847
It's what the Director calls you.

497
00:23:17,696 --> 00:23:19,297
You're nothing but a...

498
00:23:19,298 --> 00:23:21,866
It doesn't matter if you die,
you can always be replaced.

499
00:23:21,867 --> 00:23:22,947
Rei...

500
00:23:23,736 --> 00:23:25,196
The same as me.

501
00:23:33,979 --> 00:23:37,882
The Human Instrumentality Project Committee,
chaired by Kiel Lorenz,

502
00:23:37,883 --> 00:23:41,019
dissolved the research organization,
Gehirn, the next day.

503
00:23:41,020 --> 00:23:43,187
And they formed the special duty
organization, Nerv,

504
00:23:43,188 --> 00:23:45,623
as the organization that would
carry out all projects.

505
00:23:45,624 --> 00:23:49,560
All of us were moved directly into Nerv,

506
00:23:49,561 --> 00:23:54,011
with the exception of one, Dr. Akagi,
the remarkable creator of the Magi System.

507
00:23:54,833 --> 00:23:55,593
Year 2015

508
00:23:56,869 --> 00:23:59,119
Now, I guess I'll go.

509
00:24:04,543 --> 00:24:05,843
Oh, it's you.

510
00:24:05,844 --> 00:24:07,304
Long time no see.

511
00:24:07,980 --> 00:24:10,848
I've put the guards outside to sleep for a while.

512
00:24:10,849 --> 00:24:13,158
This will cost you your life.

513
00:24:14,086 --> 00:24:16,821
I just want to get closer to the truth

514
00:24:16,822 --> 00:24:18,456
within myself.

515
00:24:18,457 --> 00:24:20,591
Besides, it looks like they'll find out

516
00:24:20,592 --> 00:24:23,094
that I diverted the sample of
Adam to Commander Ikari,

517
00:24:23,095 --> 00:24:25,263
so I have to guard my own interests too,

518
00:24:25,264 --> 00:24:27,373
or various bad things will happen.

519
00:24:31,737 --> 00:24:33,637
Thank you very much for your cooperation.

520
00:24:35,374 --> 00:24:36,641
Is it over?

521
00:24:36,642 --> 00:24:38,982
Yes, the problem has been resolved, so...

522
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:42,730
I see.

523
00:24:43,782 --> 00:24:44,849
What about him?

524
00:24:44,850 --> 00:24:45,990
I do not know.

525
00:24:59,298 --> 00:25:01,198
Hey, you're late.

526
00:25:13,445 --> 00:25:14,435
I'm home.

