00:25:54,286 --> 00:25:55,896
Katsuragi, it's me.

530
00:25:56,855 --> 00:25:59,057
I've probably put you through a lot of trouble

531
00:25:59,058 --> 00:26:01,198
by the time you're listening to this.

532
00:26:02,227 --> 00:26:03,628
I'm sorry.

533
00:26:03,629 --> 00:26:05,738
Tell Ritchan I said I'm sorry too.

534
00:26:06,498 --> 00:26:08,800
Also, since I've troubled you so much anyway,

535
00:26:08,801 --> 00:26:11,235
there's this flower I've been growing...

536
00:26:11,236 --> 00:26:13,426
I1t'd make me happy if you'd water it for me.

537
00:26:14,706 --> 00:26:16,406
Shinji knows where it is.

538
00:26:17,709 --> 00:26:20,669
Katsuragi, the truth is with you.

539
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:23,260
Go forward without any hesitation.

540
00:26:24,550 --> 00:26:27,070
If I ever get to see you again,

541
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:30,030
I'll say the words I wasn't able
to say eight years ago.

542
00:26:31,090 --> 00:26:32,690
Bye.

543
00:26:32,691 --> 00:26:35,001
Message recorded at 12:02pm.

544
00:26:38,363 --> 00:26:39,703
Jerk...

545
00:26:40,933 --> 00:26:43,513
You're really such a jerk...

546
00:27:06,458 --> 00:27:09,998
Right then, all I could do was
run away from Misato.

547
00:27:11,597 --> 00:27:15,107
There was nothing I could do or say.
I was a child.

548
00:27:17,469 --> 00:27:18,669
It made me realize that.

